# Gmail

IMAPAccount gmail
Host imap.gmail.com
User pemacsmail1@gmail.com
PassCmd "gpg2 -q --for-your-eyes-only --no-tty -d ~/.mailpass-gmail.gpg"
AuthMechs LOGIN
SSLType IMAPS
SSLVersions TLSv1.2
CertificateFile /usr/local/etc/openssl/certs/gmail.crt
CertificateFile /usr/local/etc/openssl/certs/google.crt
CertificateFile /usr/local/etc/openssl/certs/Equifax.crt

IMAPStore gmail-remote
Account gmail

MaildirStore gmail-local
Path ~/.mail/gmail/
Inbox ~/.mail/gmail/Inbox

Channel gmail
Master :gmail-remote:
Slave :gmail-local:
# Exclude everything under the internal [Gmail] folder, except the interesting folders
Patterns * ![Gmail]* "[Gmail]/All Mail"
Create Both
SyncState *

